                                <p align="left" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; color: #58585A; padding:0in .1in .1in .1in;"> 
                                     Dear {!relatedTo.Direct_Sales_Rep__r.Name},
                                </p>
                                <p align="left" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; color: #58585A; padding:0in .1in .1in .1in;">
                                   An NCR Channel Partner {!relatedTo.Partner_Contact__r.Name} has submitted a Deal Registration for an opportunity with the following customer {!relatedTo.End_Customer_Account_name__r.Name}, where you are listed as the Account Owner in Sales Force. This is only for the opportunity, not the customer account.
                                </p>
                                 <p  align="left" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; color: #58585A;padding:0in .1in .0in .1in; " >
                  
                                   This message is to notify you of the Deal Registration and its number {! relatedTo.Name}. You can click on the above link which will take you to the details of the Deal Registration in Sales Force.
                                </p>
                                
                                 <p  align="left" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; color: #58585A;padding:0in .1in .0in .1in; " >
                                    <b>Your Actions Required: </b>  
                                    
                                </p>
                                <p  align="left" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; color: #58585A;padding:0in .1in .0in .1in; " >
                                     
                                    <ul  style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #58585A;">
                                      <li style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;  color: #58585A;">Contact Sales Operations {! relatedTo.Queue_Mailbox__c} and the Channel Account Manager {!relatedTo.NCR_Account_Manager__r.Name}, {!relatedTo.NCR_Account_Manager__r.Email} of the channel partner regarding the disposition of this opportunity.  </li>
                                      <li style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;  color: #58585A;">The NCR Channel Account Manager has a role and responsibility to understand and receive either an approval or rejection from you regarding if their channel partner can continue to pursue this deal with customer {!relatedTo.End_Customer_Account_name__r.Name}.</li>
                                      <li style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;  color: #58585A;">The discussion objectives are to determine if this channel partner can work with Direct sales or continue with the on this own. You must coordinate and work with the CAM to negotiate and determine a mutual decision for this opportunity.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </p>
                                                                            
                               <p align="left" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; color: #58585A; padding:0in .1in .1in .1in;">
